Private implementation classes for the Jsr330Activator.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Injection
    Defines an injection point in a provider class.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InjectionBase
    Contains methods shared between Injection implementations.
    InjectionField
    An Injection implementation that operates on a provider field.
    InjectionMethod
    Implementation of Injection that injects using a method.
    ProviderAdapter
    This class defines the operations done by the Jsr330Activator on the Provider implementations found inside the bundle.

Package no.steria.osgi.jsr330activator.implementation Description

Private implementation classes for the Jsr330Activator. These classes are not exported from the OSGi bundle version of the Jsr330Activator
Author:
Steinar Bang
